  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Version Notes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is an outdated version of the game and is not recommended for new players.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Switch to the New Version</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As a reward for veteran players, the game will be synced with the version of <CultivationMagicWorld>. After the initial sync, subsequent syncs will only occur when major updates are released.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>(Achievements and cloud saves are not available in this version)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In your Steam Library, right-click the game: **Properties** -> **Betas** -> Enter the code: 123456789666 -> **Confirm**.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>XiuzhenWorld2</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《XiuzhenWorld2》is a 3D world where your goal is to level up from a mere mortal into an immortal at the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its a semi-idle game with fun immortal cultivation mechanics such as</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- leveling up to become stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- capturing monsters as pets to fight for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- killing monsters & comparing the stats of different equipment loot you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- over 10 different combat skills which get unlocked as you level up to kill monsters even faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- upgrading your weapons to become more powerful with currency you collect from monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- opening treasure chests which drop from monsters, these treasure chests provide random drops, see how lucky you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Reincarnation to come back stronger with better base stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The game comes with a built-in AFK(Away From Keybourd) function.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Version Notes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is an outdated version of the game and is not recommended for new players.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Switch to the New Version</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As a reward for veteran players, the game will be synced with the version of <CultivationMagicWorld>. After the initial sync, subsequent syncs will only occur when major updates are released.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>(Achievements and cloud saves are not available in this version)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In your Steam Library, right-click the game: **Properties** -> **Betas** -> Enter the code: 123456789666 -> **Confirm**.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>XiuzhenWorld2</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《XiuzhenWorld2》is a 3D world where your goal is to level up from a mere mortal into an immortal at the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its a semi-idle game with fun immortal cultivation mechanics such as</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- leveling up to become stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- capturing monsters as pets to fight for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- killing monsters & comparing the stats of different equipment loot you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- over 10 different combat skills which get unlocked as you level up to kill monsters even faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- upgrading your weapons to become more powerful with currency you collect from monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- opening treasure chests which drop from monsters, these treasure chests provide random drops, see how lucky you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Reincarnation to come back stronger with better base stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The game comes with a built-in AFK(Away From Keybourd) function.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
